dct_description_sm: Ioannes Temporarius faciebat blesis anno Messiae nati 1592. Epoche Christianae 1590. Mundi 5610.
Bar scale on map given in "Lieues".
Monogram, bottom left: "GT fe.": G[abriel] T[avernier] fe.[cit].
Appears in Bouguereau's Le theatre Francoys, 1594.
